title: Microsoft Office ProPlus 2013 SP1 VL x86 en-US February 2016
description:
****************************************************
Microsoft Office ProPlus 2013 SP1 VL x86 en-US February 2016
****************************************************

System requirements

Windows 10/8.1/8,7 SP1 + Server/Server 2012 R2/2012/Server 2008 R2

Release Info

- Language: en-US
- Channel: Volume License
- Version: 15.0.4763.1000
- File Format: DAA (compressed ISO file
- Includes all updates published by February 9, 2016

Installation

- Unzip ProPlus15.X86.SP1.en-US-2016.02
- If you know how to handle DAA files, just go ahead (delete Makeiso batch file + piso.exe and PowerISO.exe)
- If you don't: run the batch file Makeiso (this will convert the DAA file to ISO and delete intermediary files)
- Mount or burn ISO file and install Office
- Install Visual Studio for Office Runtime from add-ins folder (required update)
- Activate using Microsoft Toolkit 2.5.3 (in add-ins folder, click the Office button, install AutoKMS, and click the Activate button)

Bonus (Add-ins folder)

- Classic Menu for Office v5.85 + serial
- Office Tab v9.81 + serial
- Merge reg file 'Remove Sign In icon Office 2013' to remove the "Sign in" option

Please SEED for a while!
